displayName: Fotizona Residential Area Adventurer's Guild - Ftera Dormitory Melos' Room

parameters: Clea: Let's go ahead and talk.

Girl Ect: ...I don't know anyone who would leave their
daughter and hide in a cave!

Hole-digging Melos: When you say that... well, I brought
along the child of an adventurer I mentioned before!
Girl Ect: Hmm, I won't be swayed by something like that!

Hole-digging Melos: The weather is nice today, let's play
together in the courtyard!
Girl Ect: Well, if Papa insists...
Girl Ect: Mmm... I'm sorry, Papa.

Melos the Hole Digger: I'm the one who should apologize.
Take your time to rest and let's play together again.
Melos the Hole Digger: Thank you, you saved me.
Melos the Hole Digger: I'm sorry for being so busy today.

Melos the Hole Digger: I have plans to see a doctor soon.
I'm a little worried considering what happened today...

Clea: If there's anything I can do to help, please let me
know.
Melos the Hole Digger: Thank you... Ect will be happy too.
Young girl Ect: Huh... it's not Papa... Clea-san...?

Young girl Ect: I was trying to change because I was
sweating... and then...
Clea: Don't worry, I'll do it.

Young girl Ect: Ah... it feels so good... Thank you for
coming even though you're busy.
Clea: Don't worry. Is your body okay?

Young girl Ect: ...I've been sleeping a lot because of the
fever. I actually wanted to go outside and help Papa.

Young girl Ect: I want to get better soon and go on various
explorations.
Clea: Let's go together once you're feeling better.

Young girl Ect: Yeah, I'm definitely going to become an
adventurer! And then I'll help Papa with his research.

Clea: In that case, please make sure to eat well and get
plenty of rest.

Young girl Ect: Mom got sick and couldn't recover from the
fever, she gradually became weaker and...

Young girl Ect: I'm scared... I'm just like I was before...
If things stay like this... Papa will be all alone...

Clea: Don't worry... Ect-chan, you won't die. You won't
break the promise with me, right?
Young girl Ect: Yeah... thank you, Clea-san
Shall I give you a small HP recovery leaf?

Melos the Digger: I'll ask for a recovery leaf. You should
be able to buy it at the tool shop.

Melos the Hole Digger: It seems like she can't get up
easily.
